oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Christmas Village at State Fairgrounds (19169)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Christmas; Holidays; woodcuts;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (red and green on brown) announcing a Christmas Village at the State Fairgrounds on November 13, 14, and 15.
